cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this dataset, please cite it as below."
title: "Generative Matter V3: An open dataset of AI-generated synthetic materials for architecture"
abstract: >-
  Approximately 120,000 candidate compositions derived from Google DeepMind's GNoME
  stable-materials corpus, each carrying an AI-drafted workshop recipe, scored and filtered
  for architectural use, and narrowed to the 245 materials published in the Synthetic Types
  Atlas (2026). Five layered, documented, machine-readable tables (JSONL + Parquet).
